					"type": 23,
					"value": "Buyer1, a halfling, Pheebs Splayfoot. Steeps calculation: multiple buyers negotiate with a merchant on the price of their goods. The merchant is pretty much fleecing them, but they'll make a killing re-selling the explosive materials once the fight starts proper, and they know it."
